Title: '  Indonesia is charming'
DateModified: '2019-02-01'
DatePublished: '2019-02-01'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/indonesia-is-charming
SetInCountry: Indonesia
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Ahmed Abbas
AuthorCountry: Sudan
Text: "bada'at qusatay fi shahr fibrayir lileam 2018 limuhawalat aiskitshaf wahidat\
  \ min 'akbar buldan alqarat al'asiawia .tajualat fiha bayn alhadathat waltabieat\
  \ alrrayiea .wrayat fiha altanawue althaqafiu wamadaa hubi alandwnysyn lilsiyahat\
  \ waistiqbal alzuwwar . kanat min 'ajmal albuldan alty zarataha fi hayati lidha\
  \ 'atlaqat ealayha 'iindunisia balad alsihr\n\n\u0639\u0631\u0636 \u0627\u0644\u0645\
  \u0632\u064A\u062F\n\nI started my story in February of 2018 to try to discover\
  \ one of the largest countries in the Asian continent. I traveled between modernity\
  \ and wonderful nature. I saw the cultural diversity and the Indonesian love of\
  \ tourism and the reception of visitors.\nIt was one of the most beautiful countries\
  \ I have ever visited\nSo Indonesia called it the country of magic"
